      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="1924_AS_RBH_1_00002"/><rs ref="#pmb41240" type="place">Austria</rs></addrLine><addrLine>Herrn</addrLine><addrLine>Dr. Richard Beer-Hofma<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c></addrLine><addrLine><rs type="place" ref="#pmb68">Wien XVIII</rs></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb235251" type="place">Hasenauerstr 59</rs></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="image"><p rend="center"><pb facs="1924_AS_RBH_1_00001"/><hi rend="pre-print"><rs ref="#pmb12589" type="place">Celerina</rs></hi></p></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="right"><pb facs="1924_AS_RBH_1_00002"/><date when="1924-08-18">18. 8. 24</date></dateline></opener><p><salute>lieber Richard,</salute> ob dieser Gru<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>s Sie noch in <rs ref="#pmb50" type="place">Wien</rs> finden mag? – Hier ist’s so herrlich wie nur je; Ende der
               Woche fahre ich weiter, – <rs ref="#pmb967" type="place">Luzern</rs>? <rs ref="#pmb40405" type="place">Berner Oberland</rs>? <rs ref="#pmb885" type="place">Lugano</rs>? – Heut besuchen mich <rs ref="#pmb11324 #pmb2657" type="person">Fi<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chers</rs> (aus <rs ref="#pmb40407" type="place">Flims</rs>.) <rs ref="#pmb2238" type="person">Lili</rs> u <rs ref="#pmb2173" type="person">Olga</rs> sind in <rs ref="#pmb41063" type="place">Zuoz</rs> (nah von hier) <rs ref="#pmb12692" type="person">Heini</rs> schon abgereist. Alles herzliche Ihnen
               und den Ihrigen</p><closer>Ihr <signed>Arthur</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
